presetCouncils.name: Research Team
presetCouncils.description: Top arena models from 5 providers: Opus 4.6 (#1, 1M) + Gemini 3 Pro (#3, 1M) + Grok 4.1 Fast (#4, 2M) + GPT-5.1 (#11, 400K) + GLM-5 (#12, 205K). Opus 4.6 leads as #1 arena model.
presetCouncils.simpleDescription: Your dream team of AI brains. They all think about your question, check each other's work, then the lead writes the final answer.

presetCouncils.name: Model Arena
presetCouncils.description: Opus 4.6 vs Gemini 3 Pro vs Grok 4.1 vs GPT-5.1 — top 4 arena models compete, you pick the winner
presetCouncils.simpleDescription: Four top paid AIs compete on every question. You see all their answers and pick the winner.

presetCouncils.name: Agent Pipeline
presetCouncils.description: GPT-5.1 + Gemini 3 Pro + Grok 4.1 Fast respond, Opus 4.6 (#1 arena) refines into one polished answer
presetCouncils.simpleDescription: Each AI improves the previous one's answer like a relay race. The last one polishes it into the best version.

presetCouncils.name: Smart Router
presetCouncils.description: Opus 4.6 (#1 arena) routes to Gemini 3 Pro, Grok 4.1 Fast, or GPT-5.1
presetCouncils.simpleDescription: Automatically picks the best AI for each question. Math goes to one, writing to another, coding to a third.

presetCouncils.name: Side-by-Side
presetCouncils.description: Opus 4.6 vs Gemini 3 Pro vs Grok 4.1 vs GPT-5.1 — top 4 arena models head to head
presetCouncils.simpleDescription: See how the top 4 AIs answer the same question, side by side. Great for comparing who's best at what.

presetCouncils.name: Pro Debate
presetCouncils.description: Gemini 3 Pro + GPT-5.1 argue opposing sides, Opus 4.6 (#1 arena) moderates
presetCouncils.simpleDescription: Top paid AIs argue opposite sides of your question. A moderator analyzes both sides and delivers the verdict.

presetCouncils.name: Expert Panel
presetCouncils.description: Opus 4.6 + Gemini 3 Pro + Grok 4.1 + GPT-5.1 + GLM-5 vote on the best answer
presetCouncils.simpleDescription: Five top AIs from different providers all answer, then vote on the best response. The most popular answer wins.
